      <title>肯尼亚财政部敦促在高借贷利率下严格财政纪律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/kenya-treasury-urges-fiscal-discipline-amid-high-borrowing-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于国内利率过高导致借贷成本高昂，肯尼亚财政部呼吁加强公共资源的使用纪律。]]></description>
