      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:22:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洪水使捷克 18 亿美元紧缩计划受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/czech-government-plans-to-boost-budget-deficit-due-to-floods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国计划今年和明年增加财政赤字，以应对大面积洪水造成的损失，这对政府控制国家债务的雄心又一次打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/czech-government-plans-to-boost-budget-deficit-due-to-floods</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 08:49:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲电动汽车销量暴跌，汽车制造商寻求欧盟援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-19/europe-s-august-car-sales-fall-16-5-yoy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月份，德国电动汽车市场暴跌，导致欧洲整体汽车市场出现下滑。欧洲汽车制造商协会敦促欧盟委员会在 2025 年实现汽车排放目标之前采取紧急救济措施。彭博社的 Oliver Crook 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-19/europe-s-august-car-sales-fall-16-5-yoy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 07:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲电动汽车销量暴跌 车企寻求欧盟援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/germany-s-slump-in-ev-sales-drags-on-europe-s-auto-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国电动汽车市场上个月暴跌，导致欧洲整体电动汽车市场出现下滑，迫使汽车制造商呼吁布鲁塞尔重新考虑关键的气候目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/germany-s-slump-in-ev-sales-drags-on-europe-s-auto-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
